                "verified_badge_text": "Verified Customer",
                "label_text": "All-day energy",
                "review_text": "<p>I've tried every energy supplement under the sun and nothing stuck - until these. By week three I was waking up ready to go, no afternoon crash, no jitters. The Ashwagandha and Shilajit combo just quietly does its job. My workouts feel stronger and my focus at work is noticeably sharper. One gummy a day really is all it takes.</p>"
