                "review_text": "<p>I picked these up primarily for the stress support - the Ashwagandha was a big draw - and they've exceeded my expectations on every front. My skin looks clearer, my sleep is deeper, and my energy through the day is much more balanced. The gummies taste great too, which means I actually remember to take them.</p>"
